When you send me an email: 
1. put your name and class in the subject line (e.g. Hanako Suzuki, Theme 9); 
2. begin your email with: “Dear Professor Rowley”; 
3. end your email with: “Sincerely” followed by your name; 
4. write in English. I do not answer emails from students in Japanese.
